 services</a> to small and mid-sized businesses. Services include contract drafting, contract revision and dispute resolution.","As a contract drafter, McGrath &amp; Spielberger provides consultation and contract-drafting services related to business formation, partnership agreements, mergers and acquisitions, buy-sell agreements, employment agreements and non-compete agreements. These contract-drafting services blend business consultation and legal advice to both startups and established businesses that don’t have these contracts in place, or would like to revise contracts that are already in place.","For startups, McGrath and Spielberger offers contract law services that extend from business origination to buy-sell agreements. Attorneys advise clients on the benefits and drawbacks of being a limited liability company, a non-profit or a for-profit corporation — and then complete the required legal documents. Startups can also receive commercial lease negotiation services from McGrath &amp; Spielberger to obtain, transfer or exit a lease. Partnership, operating, ownership and shareholder agreements are also a component of contract law covered by McGrath and Spielberger. These contracts define outline key business components like operations, ownership and liability.","McGrath &amp; Spielberger offers contract-drafting services and contract-revision services to established businesses as well. These services include the drafting or revising of independent contractor agreements, which can help businesses minimize exposure to liability. Business owners can also turn to McGrath &amp; Spielberger to negotiate and enforce debt collection agreements, and to define and revise terms of marketing agreements. For conflict resolution, McGrath &amp; Spielberger offers contract review, negotiation and consultation services pertaining to internal or external company disputes. The law firm also generates demand letters in the process of dispute resolution.","McGrath &amp; Spielberger represents clients in Florida, Georgia, North Carolina, Ohio, South Carolina and Tennessee. In addition to its contract services, the law firm also provides business owners with copyright and tax law services. The firm provides limited scope legal counseling through phone calls, email and in-person visits, as well as full-scope services that include business litigation, commercial debt collection and asset sales and purchases for small and medium-sized business owners."]},"id":"6bd530d4-a4e1-4cf6-a9da-d920b7186865","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_67189","url":"/mcgrath-and-spielberger-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-contributor","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-contributor","dateCreated":"2019-04-12T16:48:24Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Contributor","dateModified":"2019-04-12T16:48:24Z","id":"w5zRTt8zKNM8ERYhxFTX9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-10-06T14:45:46Z","datePublished":"2015-10-06T14:45:46Z","name":"McGrath & Spielberger","synopsis":"McGrath & Spielberger offers contract law and business consulting services to small and mid-sized businesses. Services include contract drafting, contract revision and dispute resolution.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"McGrath & Spielberger offers contract law and business consulting services to small and mid-sized businesses. Services include contract drafting, contract revision and dispute resolution.","language":"en","dateModified":"2015-10-06T14:45:46Z","id":"ohXLGGcnKNqQ4rYgW789E","meta":{"title":"McGrath & Spielberger Review | Top Ten Reviews","description":"McGrath &amp; Spielberger provides business contract services and business consulting services to small and medium-sized businesses throughout the country."},"products":[{"slug":"mcgrath-and-spielberger","url":"/product/mcgrath-and-spielberger","dateCreated":"2019-04-12T20:23:26Z","name":"McGrath & Spielberger","dateModified":"20